---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="What is a Ruck Club" description="Learn about the concept and purpose of ruck clubs">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What is a Ruck Club</h1>
  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
      <p>A ruck club is a group of individuals who come together to participate in rucking, which is walking with a weighted backpack. This activity builds strength, endurance, and camaraderie.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Core Principles</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Inclusivity: Welcoming individuals of all fitness levels and backgrounds.</li>
        <li>Safety: Prioritizing proper form and injury prevention.</li>
        <li>Consistency: Regular meetings to build habit and progress.</li>
        <li>Community: Fostering a supportive and motivating environment.</li>
        <li>Purpose: Aligning rucking with personal and collective goals.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Practical Checklist</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Define the club's mission and goals.</li>
        <li>Choose a regular meeting time and location.</li>
        <li>Establish safety guidelines and equipment requirements.</li>
        <li>Create a communication channel (e.g., WhatsApp group, email list).</li>
        <li>Plan the first ruck event and invite participants.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Downloadable Checklist</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/checklists/what-is-a-ruck-club.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" download>
          Download Printable Checklist (PDF)
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
